Before the trial started Curtin, 20, and Groake, 25, pleaded guilty to conspiracy to rob Selfridges.Last July, Groake was sentenced to eight years and Curtin to 13 years in jail.

Curtin also pleaded guilty to conspiracy to rob the Windsor jewellery and has yet to be sentenced.

Kris Monaghan, 25, and Ian Rawlings, 31, pleaded guilty to conspiracy to rob Selfridges at an earlier hearing and also await sentence.

